        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          This comprehensive checklist is designed to guide you through the various phases of your relocation, helping you stay organized and ensuring you do not miss any critical tasks. Whether you are in the early planning stages or have just arrived, this guide aims to provide practical advice and resources.
        </p>
